  sequenceId: DAY4_OPENING
  sequenceTitle: Day4_Opening
  description: "Cu\u1ED1i ng\xE0y 3, sinh vi\xEAn trao \u0111\u1ED5i xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n
    v\xE0 m\u1EDF \u0111\u1EA7u ng\xE0y 4."
